            "title": "港股開升65點阿里反彈  海偉首掛挫逾半成  波司登跌近3.8%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">港股恒生指數開升65點或0.25%，報26011，恒生科技指數升24點或0.43%，報5622點，恒生國企指數升31點或0.34%，報9196點。大市成交15.58億元。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"海偉股份招股書封面\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/11/09609.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"海偉股份招股書封面\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/11/09609.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">海偉股份招股書封面</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">海偉股份(09609)首掛，挫5.46%，報13.5元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">友邦(01299)低開0.61%，報81.55元，成交居首，阿里(09988)升0.8%，報151.8元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">中芯(00981)升1.83%，報69.6元 華虹(01347)升0.83%，報73.15元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">紫金礦業(02899)升1.82%，報31.26元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">寧德(03750)升1.02%，報474.8元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">波司登(03998)中期溢利上升5.3%，派中期股息每股6.3港仙。股價開跌3.79%，報4.83元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">麗新國際(00191)及麗新發展(00488)，稱出售事宜磋商中，股價無升跌，麗國報0.55元，麗展0.65元。</p>\n</div>",
